{
  "stem": "6257.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I and my sister played in this courtyard with other children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We used to have this one bicycle which all the children shared.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I remember.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And yes, I remember we-- it was quite a reasonably happy time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And yes, my mother also had a sister-- younger sister called-- called Bella, who lived there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the aunt who was married to my mother's brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was the-- not the pianist, she was the rhythmic teacher, the dancer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and then there was the brother who was very resourceful.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He also worked in the factory and seemed somehow to look after the family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was an old lady living there, rather mysterious, a sort of lodger, who was not really Jewish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she was a cripple, and she-- she-- she wouldn't leave the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She had nowhere to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some mysterious-- and she was killed eventually by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But anyway, that time she was still living and teaching languages to everybody, my cousins, and French, and Russian, and German.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's a strange memory, this old woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know who she was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Apart from this woman, we were just the family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know that a lot of Jews were thrown out quite soon from the smaller towns around Warsaw, and thrown into Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they didn't-- we didn't share a flat with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No, they didn't live with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she was-- she had been a headmistress of the school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that school, the hall was still there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were running soup kitchens for children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because there were these-- I don't know if they were charitable organizations.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They got some-- I don't know where they got their money from-- [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "JOINT ?] from America.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
